      "html": "<div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content=\"\"><h2 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\">Who is Love More?</h2><p class=\"sqsrte-large\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\">We're a warm-hearted community here to lead you on a self-love journey through movement, community, and connection. Through our classes, events, trainings, retreats, and healing services, our mission is to embrace the art of learning to LOVE MORE.&nbsp;<br>So welcome to the Love More family! It’s about finding your people, rooting into your authentic self, and exploring your potential. We’re here to support you every step of the way!&nbsp;</p></div>\n\n  \n</div></div>",
      "text": "Who is Love More?We're a warm-hearted community here to lead you on a self-love journey through movement, community, and connection. Through our classes, events, trainings, retreats, and healing services, our mission is to embrace the art of learning to LOVE MORE. So welcome to the Love More family! It’s about finding your people, rooting into your authentic self, and exploring your potential. We’re here to support you every step of the way!"
    },
